=== Purchase Information ===
Product Title: Eyebrow Stencils & Eyebrow Pencil, 10 Styles of Eyebrow Shaper, Reusable Eyebrow Template with Dark Brown Dual-Ended Pencil & Eyebrow Razor, 3 Minutes Makeup, Suitable For All Face Shape
Review Date: 2022/07/14
Store: VIAMAZ
Average Rating: 3.7
Product Details: {'Brand': 'VIAMAZ', 'Item Form': 'Pencil', 'Finish Type': 'Natural', 'Special Feature': 'Reusable', 'Material Feature': 'Reusable, Natural', 'Package Dimensions': '6.61 x 1.97 x 0.75 inches; 1.13 Ounces'}
Review Text: The stencils work well, and the pencil works though not easily. The small razor didn’t do much, and when putting on the safety cover, it broke. I wasn’t impressed at all with the razor. I used wax strips with the kit, and I’m happy with the results. I wish I had done a before and after picture. I have always had bushy eyebrows. I’ve never got the results I want from professionals. I took a bit too much off, but it is probably the best results I’ve had. So if you want to use stencils to try to get a good shape, this kit will work. You will want a better razor, though. I gave up on using it. Then it broke so easily. I am pleased with the final results.
Review Title: It’s ok
Rating: 3.0
